senselogic.sitevision.api.render.velocity

Interface VelocityAccess.SearchResultConstants

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SearchResult
    Enclosing interface:
    VelocityAccess

    public static interface VelocityAccess.SearchResultConstants
    Get methods for accessing field constants defined in SearchResult.

    The sole purpose of this interface is to provide access to SearchResult constants in Velocity, e.g: $searchResult.STATUS_OK
